Hilal Browser: add bang customization settings UI

Adds a dedicated HilalBangs module and a Bangs settings groupbox in
the Hilal preferences pane, allowing users to view default bangs and
add/remove custom bang definitions.

diff --git a/browser/modules/moz.build b/browser/modules/moz.build
